id=\"252\">Precision Engineering</h3>\n            <p class=\"text-white/40 text-lg leading-relaxed max-w-md ml-auto\" data-kid=\"253\">Every component in our machinery is tested for the toughest agricultural environments through deep learning simulations.</p>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"relative z-10 w-32 h-32 flex items-center justify-center shrink-0\" data-kid=\"254\">\n             <div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-[var(--emerald)]/10 rounded-full animate-pulse\" data-kid=\"255\"></div>\n             <div class=\"relative w-20 h-20 bg-white/5 rounded-full border-2 border-[var(--emerald)] flex items-center justify-center shadow-[0_0_20px_rgba(80,200,120,0.4)]\" data-kid=\"256\">\n               <i class=\"ti ti-settings-automation text-[var(--emerald)] text-4xl\" data-kid=\"257\"></i>\n             </div>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"lg:w-1/2 text-left\" data-kid=\"258\">\n            <div class=\"lg:hidden mb-6\" data-kid=\"259\">\n              <h3 class=\"text-3xl font-black font-heading text-white mb-3\" data-kid=\"260\">Precision Engineering</h3>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"glass-dark p-12 rounded-[3.5rem] hover:border-[var(--emerald)]/50 transition-all group relative overflow-hidden\" data-kid=\"261\">\n              <div class=\"absolute -top-12 -right-12 w-32 h-32 bg-[var(--emerald)]/5 rounded-full blur-2xl group-hover:bg-[var(--emerald)]/10 transition-all\" data-kid=\"262\"></div>\n              <h4 class=\"text-2xl font-black text-white mb-4 flex items-center gap-3\" data-kid=\"263\">\n                <span class=\"w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-[var(--emerald)]\" data-kid=\"264\"></span>\n                On-Field Support\n              </h4>\n              <p class=\"text-white/60 leading-relaxed font-medium\" data-kid=\"265\">Our technicians reach your farm within 6 hours of any breakdown report. We ensure zero downtime during critical harvesting periods.</p>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n\n        \n        <div class=\"flex flex-col lg:flex-row items-center gap-20\" data-kid=\"266\">\n          <div class=\"lg:w-1/2 text-right order-2 lg:order-1\" data-kid=\"267\">\n             <div class=\"bg-white/5 p-10 rounded-[3rem] border border-white/10 hover:border-[var(--emerald)]/50 transition-all\" data-kid=\"268\">\n              <h4 class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-[var(--emerald)] mb-4\" data-kid=\"269\">Lifetime Partnership</h4>\n              <p class=\"text-white/70 leading-relaxed\" data-kid=\"270\">We don't just sell tools; we offer continuous training on modern farming techniques to all our long-term customers.</p>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"relative z-10 w-24 h-24 bg-white/5 rounded-full border border-white/20 flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 order-1 lg:order-2\" data-kid=\"271\">\n             <div class=\"w-16 h-16 bg-[var(--amber)] rounded-full flex items-center justify-center shadow-lg shadow-[var(--amber)]/20\" data-kid=\"272\">\n               <i class=\"ti ti-shield-check text-[var(--evergreen)] text-4xl\" data-kid=\"273\"></i>\n             </div>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"lg:w-1/2 text-left hidden lg:block order-3\" data-kid=\"274\">\n            <h3 class=\"text-4xl font-black font-heading text-white mb-4\" data-kid=\"275\">Certified Quality</h3>\n            <p class=\"text-white/60 text-lg\" data-kid=\"276\">ISO 9001:2015 certified hardware that meets international safety and performance standards.</p>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n\n        \n        <div class=\"flex flex-col lg:flex-row items-center gap-20\" data-kid=\"277\">\n          <div class=\"lg:w-1/2 text-right hidden lg:block\" data-kid=\"278\">\n            <h3 class=\"text-4xl font-black font-heading text-white mb-4\" data-kid=\"279\">Green Logistics</h3>\n            <p class=\"text-white/60 text-lg\" data-kid=\"280\">Our delivery fleet is transitioning to 100% electric to match our solarpunk vision.</p>\